\id PHM
\h Filimun
\toc1 Filimun
\toc2 Filimun
\toc3 Flmn.
\mt1 Filimun
\c 1
\s1 Aseǧem ɣar umezwaru d tẓaǧit n uqadi
\m 
\v 1 Bulus, ameḥbus n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, d tawmat Timutiyu, i Filimun iɛizzen wenni d amsexxar akidneɣ, \f ◼ \fr 1:1 \ft \bd afessar\bd* - tanita d ict n tebrat i yuri rrasul Bulus ɣar umeddukkeř nnes Filimun x ijj n uḥenjir qqaren as ‘Unisimus’. Unisimus tuɣa-t qbeř d ismeɣ n Filimun. Yarweř zi Filimun u awarni man aya issen i-t rrasul Bulus di řeḥbes, u idweř Unisimus d řmumen (inneɣni qqaren as ‘Wanisamu’). Uřa d Filimun tuɣa idweř d řmumen x ttebcir n Bulus. Řexxu rrasul Bulus issekk-dd Unisimus ɣar Filimun ḥima ad din yiři weṣřaḥ jar asen am wawmaten di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Afa. 3:1; 4:1. \x*
\v 2 i \add učmatneɣ\add* Apfiya iɛizzen, i Arxippus, wenni d amsexxar akidneɣ, u i tmesmunt di taddart nnec: \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Rum. 16:5; 1 Kur. 16:19; Kul. 4:15, 17. \x*
\v 3 arḍa d řehna ad kidwem iřin zi AREBBI, Babatneɣ, u \add zi\add* Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.
\b
\m 
\v 4 Necc ttqadiɣ AREBBI inu řebda u ttfekkareɣ dayek di tẓaǧitin inu, \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt 1 Ts. 1:2; 2 Ts. 1:3. \x*
\v 5 xzar, \add ɛad\add* zeg wami necc sřiɣ x l’iman d tayri nnec i dayek iǧan zi jjihet n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ u zi jjihet n marra imqeddasen,
\v 6 ḥima ad din yiři ijj n uqarri yuǧɣen n l’iman nnec ař ɣa tawyed řɣiǧet di řexdayem u di tussna n marra řxar i ɣarwem di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.
\v 7 Maɣar neccin aqa ɣarneɣ řefraḥet tameqqrant d ufewwej, minzi zi ssibbet n tayri nnec ttwassareyyḥen uřawen n imqeddasen.
\b
\s1 Bulus ittceffeɛ di tmesřact n Unisimus
\m 
\v 8 S uyenni, \add waxxa\add* necc ɣari taryast aṭṭas di Lmasiḥ ḥima ad cek umureɣ min icuwwaren,
\v 9 aqa necc ɣari ḥsen, di ssibbet n tayri, ad zzayek ttareɣ. Necc Bulus, aqa ayi d awessar am mammec tessned, uca řexxu ɛawed d ameḥbus n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ,
\v 10 necc ɣari ict n tutra zi jjihet n mmi Unisimus, wenni dd-jjiɣ di ssnaseř \add da di řeḥbes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Kur. 4:15. Gal. 4:19; Kul. 4:9. \x*
\v 11 Netta tuɣa war cek ineffeɛ zic, maca řexxu aqa ineffeɛ cek d nnec aṭṭas.
\v 12 Necc aqa arriɣ ac t-i-dd ɣarek, maca qbeř i-t am mmi.
\v 13 Maɣar necc mři ufiɣ iři aqa jjiɣ t danita akidi maḥend ad xafi isexxar deg wemcan nnec min da ɣa kkeɣ di ssnaseř x ssibbet n L’Injil.
\v 14 Maca necc war xseɣ ca ad ggeɣ walu břa ma i ɣa mcawareɣ akidek, ḥima tcuni i teggid war tᵉttiři s uɣiř, maca s řxaḍar.
\v 15 Minzi nican tuɣa immsebḍa xak i drus n řweqt, ḥima ad ɣarek yiři ɛawed i řebda,
\v 16 zi ssa d tsawent war iǧi ɛad am umsexxar, maca am yijjen i iǧan ktar zeg umsexxar, am wuma iɛizzen, \add i necc beɛda\add*, mahu i cek, am di ddat am di Siditneɣ!
\m 
\v 17 Mařa teǧid d amɛacar akidi \add di l’iman\add*, qebř i-t am wenni nnec.
\v 18 Mařa netta tuɣa iḍḍarri cek niɣ zeɛma dayes amarwas, egg i-t xafi!
\v 19 Necc, Bulus, uriɣ s ufus inu, aqa ad t xeǧṣeɣ! Maḥend war qqareɣ ca, aqa uřa d cek tᵉttursed ayi ixef nnec.
\v 20 Wah, \add a\add* tawmat inu, aqa ttwassareyyḥeɣ zzayek di Siditneɣ, sareyyeḥ tayri inu di Lmasiḥ.
\b
\s1 Awař ɣar uneggaru d useǧem
\m 
\v 21 Necc ttiqqeɣ ad ayi tesřid. Uriɣ ac-dd, uca ssneɣ aqa cek ad tegged mahu min d \add ac\add* iniɣ.
\v 22 Sewjed ayi amcan mani ɣa ssenseɣ, minzi ssitimeɣ ad ɣarwem dd-arezfeɣ s tẓaǧit nwem. \x ◘ \xo 1:22 \xt Fil. 1:25. \x*
\m 
\v 23 Ipafras, wenni akidi da di řeḥbes di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, aqa iseǧem xak s řehna, \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Kul. 1:7; 4:12. \x*
\v 24 uřa d Markus d Aristarxus d Dimas d Luka inni d ayi itticen afus. \x ◘ \xo 1:24 \xt Řex. 12:12, 25; 15:37; Kul. 4:10; 2 Tim. 4:11; 1 Bṭ. 5:13; Řex. 19:29; 20:4; 27:2; Kul. 4:10, 14; 2 Tim. 4:10, 11. \x*
\m 
\v 25 Arḍa n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ad yiři ak-d buḥbeř nwem. Amin! 
